powers of nature.

24:00.732 --> 24:02.776
You know, that kind of thing.

24:02.776 --> 24:06.070
- What kind of healing powers?

24:06.070 --> 24:07.741
- You don't know, huh?

24:09.741 --> 24:15.747
- I don't know much.

24:15.747 --> 24:18.708
- Mom died when Mara was
11, and my dad lost it.

24:18.708 --> 24:23.213
He moved us down here.

24:23.213 --> 24:26.841
- Sounds like
an interesting guy.

24:26.841 --> 24:28.971
- Yeah.

24:31.971 --> 24:39.187
- What's this all about, man?

24:39.187 --> 24:53.201
- Just trying to understand.

26:18.078 --> 26:23.792
- Where were you?

26:23.792 --> 26:26.800
- Your brother
showed me the cave.

26:31.800 --> 26:33.470
- Did you like it?

26:35.470 --> 26:36.138
- Yeah.

26:37.138 --> 26:38.890
I like bats.

26:38.890 --> 26:42.250
