29:12.377 --> 29:14.963
- Aaron and I are
going into town.

29:14.963 --> 29:16.966
Can I get anyone anything?

29:17.966 --> 29:19.592
- With what car?

29:19.592 --> 29:21.011
- You don't need yours, do you?

29:22.011 --> 29:23.722
- I think you should
go check out the plot

29:23.722 --> 29:25.890
