29:47.245 --> 29:48.955
cremate me,

29:48.955 --> 29:51.000
spread me in some compost.

29:52.000 --> 29:54.920
- People will be eating you.

29:55.920 --> 29:57.924
- But I'll be dead.

29:59.924 --> 30:01.384
- I know when my dad died,

30:01.384 --> 30:05.055
my mom just wanted
a place to visit.

30:05.055 --> 30:08.892
But, you see a grave, you know?

30:08.892 --> 30:11.481
You do get a sense of closure.

30:14.481 --> 30:17.527
- Yeah, that's
really good to know.

30:19.527 --> 30:22.280
- People need rituals, you know?

30:22.280 --> 30:26.993
There's a reason why
people come together when

30:26.993 --> 30:28.955
someone dies.

30:30.955 --> 30:32.290
- What's this?

30:32.290 --> 30:34.167
- It's the will.

30:34.167 --> 30:36.378
Linda's the executor.

30:36.378 --> 30:37.756
- Of course.

30:39.756 --> 30:42.135
- She lives her, Mara.
- So do you.

30:44.135 --> 30:49.265
- It's true, but
I'm okay with it.

30:49.265 --> 31:03.279
- I'm okay with it.

31:03.279 --> 31:05.241
Dad bought the tea farm.

31:06.241 --> 31:07.909
- What?

31:07.909 --> 31:08.993
- Yeah, I know.

31:08.993 --> 31:14.833
