he first told me.

31:14.833 --> 31:16.793
- Should we go?

31:16.793 --> 31:18.086
- What?

31:18.086 --> 31:19.754
- We don't need to do
everything all together.

31:19.754 --> 31:21.381
- What about the will?
- Ben, quiet.

31:21.381 --> 31:23.174
- People will soon be coming.

31:23.174 --> 31:24.676
- Yeah, what do we need?

31:24.676 --> 31:26.970
