31:26.970 --> 31:31.183
- You're not driving anywhere,
you're too fucked up.

31:32.183 --> 31:33.435
- What?
- You're on something.

31:33.435 --> 31:34.020
It's obvious to everyone.

31:35.020 --> 31:36.438
- You're not making any sense.

31:36.438 --> 31:40.113
- You're not making any sense.
- I can drive.

31:45.113 --> 31:46.532
- Thank you.

31:47.532 --> 31:51.084
