32:01.629 --> 32:03.214
- I don't know.

32:03.214 --> 32:04.549
I don't know.

32:04.549 --> 32:08.389
- Well, I'm not comfortable
with you driving.

32:11.389 --> 32:15.018
- I took a Xanax.

32:15.018 --> 32:18.229
- Just one?

32:18.229 --> 32:20.106
- Yes, just one.

32:20.106 --> 32:25.362
- I'm not doing this.

32:25.362 --> 32:26.621
Just let me.

32:34.621 --> 32:35.584
