32:39.584 --> 32:41.920
- I don't need a sponsor.

32:41.920 --> 32:47.550
- You're careful.

32:47.550 --> 32:48.225
- Sorry.

32:55.225 --> 32:56.189
- I understand.

33:01.189 --> 33:03.904
I just can't sit
and watch you do it.

33:15.286 --> 33:17.664
Is this the tea farm?

33:17.664 --> 33:19.499
- Part of it.

34:03.168 --> 34:06.254
- Looks different in here.

34:06.254 --> 34:08.340
- This was all his.

34:08.340 --> 34:11.634
