- You lied again.

35:01.434 --> 35:03.853
- Yeah, well, I'm
telling you now.

36:44.454 --> 36:46.213
- No, no, no, no.

36:53.213 --> 36:54.850
Not like this.

37:05.850 --> 37:06.396
