39:22.278 --> 39:23.698
- I'm good.

39:24.698 --> 39:27.534
- Ben, have a seat.
- Stop touching me, man.

39:27.534 --> 39:29.244
- What'd he take?
- I don't know.

39:29.244 --> 39:31.371
I just saw him drinking.

39:31.371 --> 39:34.165
- Folks are
arriving any second.

39:34.165 --> 39:36.420
